{
  "id": null,
  "uid": "system-maintenance-overview",
  "title": "System Monitoring & Maintenance Dashboard",
  "tags": ["maintenance", "monitoring", "system", "homelab", "nixos"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 36,
  "editable": true,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "style": "dark",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-6h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "row",
      "title": "ðŸŽ¯ System Health Overview",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0}
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "Overall Health Score",
      "type": "gauge",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 1},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "system:health_score:percentage",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "orientation": "auto",
        "showThresholdLabels": false,
        "showThresholdMarkers": true
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"value": 0, "color": "red"},
              {"value": 50, "color": "orange"},
              {"value": 80, "color": "yellow"},
              {"value": 95, "color": "green"}
            ]
          },
          "min": 0,
          "max": 100,
          "unit": "percent"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Active Alerts by Severity",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 18, "x": 6, "y": 1},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "count(ALERTS{alertstate=\"firing\", severity=\"critical\"})",
          "legendFormat": "Critical",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "count(ALERTS{alertstate=\"firing\", severity=\"warning\"})",
          "legendFormat": "Warning",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
              {"value": 1, "color": "orange"},
              {"value": 5, "color": "red"}
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "System Uptime",
      "type": "stat",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 5},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "node_time_seconds - node_boot_time_seconds",
          "legendFormat": "uptime"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "s"}}
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "Root Filesystem Usage",
      "type": "stat",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 5},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "100 * (node_filesystem_size_bytes{mountpoint=\"/\",fstype!=\"tmpfs\"} - node_filesystem_free_bytes{mountpoint=\"/\",fstype!=\"tmpfs\"}) / node_filesystem_size_bytes{mountpoint=\"/\",fstype!=\"tmpfs\"}",
          "legendFormat": "/"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
              {"value": 80, "color": "yellow"},
              {"value": 90, "color": "red"}
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "RAM Usage",
      "type": "stat",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 5},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "100 * (1 - (node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes / node_memory_MemTotal_bytes))",
          "legendFormat": "RAM"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
              {"value": 80, "color": "yellow"},
              {"value": 90, "color": "red"}
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "title": "CPU Metrics",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 9}
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "CPU Usage",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "gridPos": {"h": 3, "w": 4, "x": 0, "y": 10},
      "targets": [
        {"expr": "node:cpu_usage_percent:avg", "legendFormat": "CPU Usage"}
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 100,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
              {"value": 70, "color": "yellow"},
              {"value": 90, "color": "red"}
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "CPU Usage Over Time",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 4, "y": 10},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "node:cpu_usage_percent:avg",
          "legendFormat": "CPU Usage"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 100
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "CPU Load Average",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 10},
      "targets": [
        {"expr": "node_load1 / count without (cpu,mode)(node_cpu_seconds_total{mode=\"idle\"})", "legendFormat": "1m"},
        {"expr": "node_load5 / count without (cpu,mode)(node_cpu_seconds_total{mode=\"idle\"})", "legendFormat": "5m"},
        {"expr": "node_load15 / count without (cpu,mode)(node_cpu_seconds_total{mode=\"idle\"})", "legendFormat": "15m"}
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 2
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "CPU Pressure",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 18},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "rate(node_pressure_cpu_waiting_seconds_total{type=\"some\"}[5m]) * 100",
          "legendFormat": "Some processes waiting"
        },
        {
          "expr": "rate(node_pressure_cpu_waiting_seconds_total{type=\"full\"}[5m]) * 100",
          "legendFormat": "All processes blocked"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "custom": {
            "fillOpacity": 20
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Memory Pressure",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 18},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "rate(node_pressure_memory_waiting_seconds_total{type=\"some\"}[5m]) * 100",
          "legendFormat": "Some processes waiting"
        },
        {
          "expr": "rate(node_pressure_memory_waiting_seconds_total{type=\"full\"}[5m]) * 100",
          "legendFormat": "All processes blocked"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "custom": {
            "fillOpacity": 20
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
              {"value": 1, "color": "yellow"},
              {"value": 10, "color": "red"}
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Memory Metrics",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 24}
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Memory Usage Breakdown",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 16, "x": 0, "y": 25},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "node_memory_MemTotal_bytes - node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes",
          "legendFormat": "Used"
        },
        {
          "expr": "node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes",
          "legendFormat": "Available"
        },
        {
          "expr": "node_memory_Buffers_bytes",
          "legendFormat": "Buffers"
        },
        {
          "expr": "node_memory_Cached_bytes",
          "legendFormat": "Cached"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "bytes",
          "custom": {
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "stacking": {"mode": "normal"}
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Swap Usage",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 25},
      "targets": [
        {"expr": "node_swap_used_bytes", "legendFormat": "Used"},
        {"expr": "node_swap_free_bytes", "legendFormat": "Free"}
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "bytes",
          "custom": {
            "fillOpacity": 20
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Storage and Disk Metrics",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 33}
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Disk Space Usage",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 34},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "100 * (node_filesystem_size_bytes{fstype!~\"tmpfs|overlay\"} - node_filesystem_free_bytes{fstype!~\"tmpfs|overlay\"}) / node_filesystem_size_bytes{fstype!~\"tmpfs|overlay\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{mountpoint}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 100,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
              {"value": 80, "color": "yellow"},
              {"value": 90, "color": "red"}
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Inode Usage",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 34},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "(1 - node_filesystem_files_free{fstype!~\"tmpfs|overlay\"} / node_filesystem_files{fstype!~\"tmpfs|overlay\"}) * 100",
          "legendFormat": "{{mountpoint}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 100,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
              {"value": 80, "color": "yellow"},
              {"value": 90, "color": "red"}
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Disk IO Operations",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 42},
      "targets": [
        {"expr": "rate(node_disk_reads_completed_total[5m])", "legendFormat": "{{device}} reads"},
        {"expr": "rate(node_disk_writes_completed_total[5m])", "legendFormat": "{{device}} writes"}
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "iops"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "IO Pressure",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 42},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "rate(node_pressure_io_waiting_seconds_total{type=\"some\"}[5m]) * 100",
          "legendFormat": "Some processes waiting"
        },
        {
          "expr": "rate(node_pressure_io_waiting_seconds_total{type=\"full\"}[5m]) * 100",
          "legendFormat": "All processes blocked"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "custom": {
            "fillOpacity": 20
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
              {"value": 5, "color": "yellow"},
              {"value": 20, "color": "red"}
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Network Metrics",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 50}
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Network In",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "gridPos": {"h": 3, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 51},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(node_network_receive_bytes_total[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "rx"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "Bps",
          "decimals": 2
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Network Out",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "gridPos": {"h": 3, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 51},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(node_network_transmit_bytes_total[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "tx"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "Bps",
          "decimals": 2
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Network Traffic",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 51},
      "targets": [
        {"expr": "rate(node_network_receive_bytes_total[5m])", "legendFormat": "{{device}} rx"},
        {"expr": "rate(node_network_transmit_bytes_total[5m])", "legendFormat": "{{device}} tx"}
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "Bps",
          "custom": {
            "fillOpacity": 10
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Hardware and System Info",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 59}
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Temperature Sensors",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 60},
      "targets": [
        {"expr": "node_hwmon_temp_celsius", "legendFormat": "{{sensor}} {{chip}}"}
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "celsius",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"value": 0, "color": "blue"},
              {"value": 60, "color": "green"},
              {"value": 75, "color": "yellow"},
              {"value": 85, "color": "red"}
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Systemd Failed Units",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 60},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "node_systemd_units{state=\"failed\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{name}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
              {"value": 1, "color": "red"}
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Service Monitoring",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 68}
    },
    {
      "type": "status-history",
      "title": "Service Uptime History",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 69},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "up{job!~\"prometheus|node\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{job}} - {{instance}}",
          "refId": "A",
          "interval": "1m"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "showValue": "never",
        "colWidth": 0.9
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 0,
            "fillOpacity": 100
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Alert History",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 77},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "count by (severity) (ALERTS{alertstate=\"firing\"})",
          "legendFormat": "{{severity}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "fillOpacity": 70,
            "lineWidth": 2
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "critical"},
            "properties": [{"id": "color", "value": {"mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "red"}}]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "warning"},
            "properties": [{"id": "color", "value": {"mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "orange"}}]
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Maintenance Checklists",
      "collapsed": true,
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 85},
      "panels": [
        {
          "id": 501,
          "title": "Weekly Summary",
          "type": "text",
          "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 86},
          "options": {
            "mode": "markdown",
            "content": "# Weekly Tasks\n\n## Critical\n- [ ] Review all Prometheus alerts\n- [ ] Check backup completion\n- [ ] Verify storage pool health\n- [ ] Inspect certificate expiry\n- [ ] Review system logs\n\n## Routine\n- [ ] Check service status dashboard\n- [ ] Monitor resource utilization trends\n- [ ] Review network connectivity\n\n---\n**Last completed:** _[Manual entry]_"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": 502,
          "title": "Monthly Summary",
          "type": "text",
          "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 86},
          "options": {
            "mode": "markdown",
            "content": "# Monthly Tasks\n\n## System Updates\n- [ ] Apply NixOS updates\n- [ ] Update firmware\n- [ ] Review kernel changes\n\n## Storage\n- [ ] Run ZFS/Btrfs scrub\n- [ ] Test backup restore\n- [ ] Verify snapshot retention\n\n## Security\n- [ ] Audit firewall rules\n- [ ] Review SSH access logs\n- [ ] Rotate credentials\n- [ ] Check fail2ban effectiveness\n\n## Database\n- [ ] Run vacuum/analyze\n- [ ] Check index bloat\n\n---\n**Last completed:** _[Manual entry]_"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": 503,
          "title": "Quarterly Summary",
          "type": "text",
          "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 86},
          "options": {
            "mode": "markdown",
            "content": "# Quarterly Tasks\n\n## Hardware\n- [ ] Deep hardware cleaning\n- [ ] RAID consistency check\n- [ ] Replace aging components\n\n## Disaster Recovery\n- [ ] DR rehearsal/test\n- [ ] Update recovery playbooks\n- [ ] Test cold site backups\n\n## Security\n- [ ] Full access audit\n- [ ] Network device scan\n- [ ] Review security baselines\n- [ ] License compliance check\n\n## Documentation\n- [ ] Update network map\n- [ ] Review service inventory\n- [ ] Update runbooks\n\n---\n**Last completed:** _[Manual entry]_"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
